requires:
opengl     http://www.opengl.org
fltk       http://www.fltk.org
ode        http://opende.sourceforge.net/
guile      http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/guile.html
fftw       http://www.fftw.org/
portaudio  http://www.portaudio.com/
libsndfile http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/

to build, just do the old:

make 
make install

makefiles may have to be tweaked for location of libs, SCons version to 
follow. built on slackware i386
